ATURES: Valley of Río Coro-Coro, W of Serrania de Yutaje. Plateau on W side of valley. Open savanna with scattered shrubs; periodi- cally wet, surrounded by exposed sand- stone with dwarfed vegetation.

Heres: Meseta del Guaiquinima. Altiplanicie levemente inclinada hacia el S, ubicada en el sector Nor-oriental de la meseta, cerca de la cumbre. Arbustales enanos, islas arbustivas y vegetación herbácea sabnoide sobre terrenos rocosos de arenisca.

Município de Jaboticatubas: Serra do Cipó (the highest part of the long narrow Serra do Espinhaço). Along road at km 132-133 (5-6 km along road north from crossing of the stream, Rib. Andrequicé at Fazenda Palácio).
